---
---

<header class="relative w-full min-h-[85vh] flex flex-col justify-center px-6 lg:px-16 py-12 md:py-20 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/3 -translate-y-1/2 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-[#EDEAE4] rounded-full blur-3xl -z-10 opacity-70"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
    <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-6 md:space-y-8 text-left">
      <span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 border border-stone-300 rounded-full text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-500 bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-sm">
        Hypnose · Scène · Accompagnement · Aventures
      </span>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-stone-900 leading-tight tracking-tight text-balance font-normal">
        J'aide à grandir. Partout où
        <span class="italic text-stone-600">l'imagination</span>
        peut changer une vie.
      </h1>

      <p class="max-w-xl text-lg md:text-xl text-stone-600 font-light leading-relaxed">
        Hypnotiseur depuis l'adolescence, comédien, psychologue en
        formation, moniteur de ski, et éternel curieux. Je fais se croiser
        l'art, le soin et l'aventure — pour proposer des expériences où l'on
        grandit et apprend à (se) regarder autrement.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch sm:items-center gap-4 pt-4">
        <a href="/#contact" class="group px-8 py-3.5 bg-stone-900 text-[#F7F5F1] rounded-full text-sm font-medium hover:bg-stone-700 transition-colors duration-300 text-center flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          Me contacter
          <iconify-icon icon="solar:arrow-right-linear" stroke-width="1.5" class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"></iconify-icon>
        </a>
        <a href="/#qui-je-suis" class="px-8 py-3.5 border border-stone-300 text-stone-900 rounded-full text-sm font-medium hover:bg-stone-200/50 transition-colors duration-300 text-center">
          En savoir plus
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="lg:col-span-5 relative w-full h-[350px] md:h-[500px] overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-[#EDEAE4]">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534528741775-53994a69daeb?q=80&w=1000&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Portrait de Mathieu Kuntz" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-90 transition-transform duration-700 hover:scale-105" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-stone-950/25 to-transparent"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
